{"type": "article", "id": 27726, "title": "以褶皱裙为灵感的吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-03T06:59:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021450063IHU94pPGMJeuZtk.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>这款很像是一把纸扇的吊灯 <a href=\"http://www.art-tic.com/vanity.html\">Vanity</a> 是西班牙设计师 Bruno Peral Bey 以 50 年代流行的褶皱裙为灵感设计的作品。坚硬光滑的铁质灯架和柔软粗糙的纸质灯罩经过组合，带给人一种简约大气的感觉。在亮灯之后，光线还会因为褶皱产生奇特的光影变化，很适合用作装饰灯。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145003pgjzMs6HmQkFPI7R.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.14102564\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021450049k4Ap5mCPo7ROJQt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.14066496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145004IRYnKcUNiawk6PFo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.13956466\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145005zRx6I2rwL17lCXWv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1366539\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}